{"tid":1207274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好驚解放軍進場呢啲鳩野","createTime":"2019-06-12T05:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T08:53:33.000Z","uid":389,"like":924,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"3988acf197bef91ff594ce31eadfd83a40a1adaa","tid":1207274,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOvoRiq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOvoRiq.png&h=cc34a070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人網上傳呢幅圖，又傳消息話中共派解放軍落香港。我希望大家諗清楚：<br />\n<br />\n首先，香港本身有解放軍，唔使派人落黎已經可以出動。<br />\n然後，元朗隔離就係軍營，有軍車唔奇。唔好亂傳解放軍圖嚇人！<br />\n<br />\n再者，唔通解放軍會血腥鎮壓<br />\n警犬就唔可以？<br />\n要血腥鎮壓連食環都可以出動啦<br />\n<br />\n解放軍出動根本係用黎嚇人既借口，唔好儘信，要堅守。"},{"pid":"89a1c14ce6a7686ea123509e97a1d17527f0bd96","tid":1207274,"uid":92969,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"3988acf197bef91ff594ce31eadfd83a40a1adaa","tid":1207274,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOvoRiq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOvoRiq.png&h=cc34a070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人網上傳呢幅圖，又傳消息話中共派解放軍落香港。我希望大家諗清楚：<br />\n<br />\n首先，香港本身有解放軍，唔使派人落黎已經可以出動。<br />\n然後，元朗隔離就係軍營，有軍車唔奇。唔好亂傳解放軍圖嚇人！<br />\n<br />\n再者，唔通解放軍會血腥鎮壓<br />\n警犬就唔可以？<br />\n要血腥鎮壓連食環都可以出動啦<br />\n<br />\n解放軍出動根本係用黎嚇人既借口，唔好儘信，要堅守。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8b75bca5c7339512f4df75dda7b8bcc7f55c5d5f","tid":1207274,"uid":212419,"like":187,"dislike":5,"score":182,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:52:52.000Z","msg":"根本冇需要 冇可能<br />\n信嗰啲人應該都係智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陏啲就話解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7f3ecd64ce5ac125720d27f669bfff3840c5e0","tid":1207274,"uid":138625,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:53:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5ade305c